room_title: Escape room "Cell Block 9" by Great Escape of Central Texas in Killeen
room_address: 4400 E. Central Texas Expy Killeen, TX 76543
room_description: Imagine being locked up for a crime you didn't commit and are now awaiting your time in a holding cell on your way to death row. Your friends plan an elaborate scheme to get you out by breaking into the sheriff's office at night. Using nothing but your communication skills to solve the clues to find a key and unlock the jail door to get you out.
